00:01:15.775 --> 00:01:18.699
=Episode 9=
(I will be the one to protect you)

00:01:18.700 --> 00:01:21.757
(Zichen Gate)

00:01:27.220 --> 00:01:29.100
Su Jinyuan.

00:01:29.300 --> 00:01:31.900
It was you who brought shame
upon the Xiao family.

00:01:32.220 --> 00:01:35.339
And now you dare ask me for justice.

00:01:35.340 --> 00:01:38.100
Should I call you shameless,

00:01:39.340 --> 00:01:41.580
or simply reckless?

00:01:43.340 --> 00:01:44.940
Your Majesty, please discern the truth.

00:01:45.060 --> 00:01:46.539
I, Su Jinyuan,

00:01:46.540 --> 00:01:48.380
can endure such slander myself,

00:01:48.580 --> 00:01:49.860
but the Xiao family cannot.

00:01:50.312 --> 00:01:52.872
The sons of the Xiao clan
died on the battlefield,

00:01:52.950 --> 00:01:54.710
leaving behind widows and orphans.

00:01:54.860 --> 00:01:55.579
Yet now,

00:01:55.580 --> 00:01:58.020
they are left
to be bullied and humiliated.

00:02:00.460 --> 00:02:02.660
So you mean

00:02:03.500 --> 00:02:06.460
I have neglected and dishonored
those who earned merit?

00:02:09.887 --> 00:02:11.424
I have come today,

00:02:11.425 --> 00:02:13.225
only to ask for a clear decree.

00:02:13.262 --> 00:02:15.342
Let those who insult
the Xiao family know

00:02:16.100 --> 00:02:18.620
that even without sons serving at court,

00:02:18.700 --> 00:02:20.845
the Xiao clan is still
under Imperial protection.

00:02:32.740 --> 00:02:35.140
Why should I grant you favor

00:02:35.740 --> 00:02:37.860
and make an exception
for the Xiao family?

00:02:42.775 --> 00:02:44.735
The Xiao clan served loyally
for generations.

00:02:44.860 --> 00:02:46.136
What I ask today

00:02:46.137 --> 00:02:48.217
is merely a place to stand.

00:02:48.350 --> 00:02:50.259
Your Majesty's legacy
will last for ages.

00:02:50.260 --> 00:02:52.300
Though our contribution is small,

00:02:52.612 --> 00:02:54.172
it is better than none.

00:02:57.787 --> 00:03:01.307
Bold words for a woman
who fears no death.

00:03:03.820 --> 00:03:06.780
If I refuse you today,

00:03:07.220 --> 00:03:09.780
others may call me cold and unfeeling.

00:03:26.460 --> 00:03:27.860
Very well.

00:03:29.740 --> 00:03:32.060
Then I shall decree this.

00:03:33.020 --> 00:03:35.179
Your name shall be cleared.

00:03:35.180 --> 00:03:37.460
Xie Yunyan will be granted
an official post.

00:03:37.540 --> 00:03:38.780
Are you satisfied?

00:03:41.312 --> 00:03:43.819
Thanks Your Majesty
for this great grace.

00:03:43.820 --> 00:03:47.180
Long live the Emperor.

00:03:49.540 --> 00:03:51.060
This is enough?

00:03:53.820 --> 00:03:55.579
Will you return tomorrow

00:03:55.580 --> 00:03:57.380
with another request,

00:03:57.950 --> 00:04:00.350
beating the grievance drum again?

00:04:02.210 --> 00:04:04.624
I know I have offended the throne,

00:04:04.625 --> 00:04:05.905
a grave sin indeed.

00:04:06.750 --> 00:04:08.750
I accept Your Majesty's punishment.

00:04:11.925 --> 00:04:14.245
At least you know your place.

00:04:14.740 --> 00:04:16.374
Go to the palace gate,

00:04:16.375 --> 00:04:19.055
and receive the court caning yourself.

00:05:10.350 --> 00:05:11.430
You are awake.

00:05:14.180 --> 00:05:15.060
Where is she?

00:05:21.580 --> 00:05:23.460
Go meet her at the palace gate.

00:05:23.900 --> 00:05:25.300
She struck the grievance drum,

00:05:25.660 --> 00:05:27.340
and pled for justice
for the Xiao family.

00:05:54.325 --> 00:05:57.070
(Zichen Gate)

00:06:04.875 --> 00:06:06.635
If she wants the Xiao clan restored,

00:06:06.940 --> 00:06:08.940
the price she paid is worth it.

00:06:09.462 --> 00:06:10.782
I said before,

00:06:10.820 --> 00:06:12.539
I will win it myself.

00:06:12.540 --> 00:06:13.259
Let go.

00:06:13.260 --> 00:06:14.779
If you rush into the palace now,

00:06:14.780 --> 00:06:16.780
her suffering will be in vain.

