00:07:28.060 --> 00:07:29.180
Come.

00:07:29.940 --> 00:07:31.580
Let us go home.

00:07:32.712 --> 00:07:39.174
♪In the dark we wrote
one small flame of hope♪

00:07:39.175 --> 00:07:41.570
(Heaven Rewards Diligence)

00:07:44.900 --> 00:07:46.620
This was all your lousy idea.

00:07:46.780 --> 00:07:48.820
A quack who only knows
how to drug people.

00:07:53.420 --> 00:07:55.274
Young Lady Su asked me for help.

00:07:55.275 --> 00:07:56.461
How could I turn her away?

00:07:56.462 --> 00:07:58.902
So you sent her to her death instead?

00:08:03.562 --> 00:08:04.842
Are you not afraid

00:08:05.500 --> 00:08:07.300
that punishment might kill her?

00:08:07.940 --> 00:08:09.380
It should not go that far.

00:08:09.780 --> 00:08:11.540
Why did you lie to me?

00:08:16.260 --> 00:08:17.540
Young Master.

00:08:17.860 --> 00:08:19.579
You should keep her prescription safe.

00:08:19.580 --> 00:08:21.180
Shouting so fiercely like that,

00:08:21.300 --> 00:08:23.180
Young Lady Su did all this for you.

00:08:23.500 --> 00:08:25.140
Yet you scold her instead.

00:08:30.980 --> 00:08:32.620
Go and apologize.

00:08:35.700 --> 00:08:36.580
I...

00:08:37.140 --> 00:08:39.060
I did not mean it that way.

00:08:39.740 --> 00:08:41.180
I was just

00:08:41.820 --> 00:08:43.220
worried about you.

00:08:46.020 --> 00:08:46.819
You already yelled,

00:08:46.820 --> 00:08:47.979
and that is your apology?

00:08:47.980 --> 00:08:49.540
Not a trace of sincerity.

00:08:55.375 --> 00:08:57.561
I, Xie Yunyan, swear to the heavens,

00:08:57.562 --> 00:08:59.042
from this day on,

00:08:59.075 --> 00:09:01.315
if I ever speak harshly
to Su Jinyuan again,

00:09:01.437 --> 00:09:03.597
may lightning strike me down...

00:09:04.312 --> 00:09:05.432
Xie Yunyan.

00:09:05.887 --> 00:09:07.127
Shall die without peace.

00:09:07.420 --> 00:09:08.540
You...

00:09:13.787 --> 00:09:16.419
Saying that to your sister-in-law

00:09:16.420 --> 00:09:18.300
sounds a bit strange.

00:09:30.900 --> 00:09:32.340
Actually, I...

00:09:32.740 --> 00:09:34.820
What I meant was,

00:09:34.860 --> 00:09:36.820
from now on,

00:09:36.837 --> 00:09:39.117
I will never let you
be hurt because of me.

00:09:39.525 --> 00:09:41.165
Nor will I

00:09:41.325 --> 00:09:43.085
fail your efforts again.

00:09:47.420 --> 00:09:50.260
That somehow sounds

00:09:50.820 --> 00:09:52.340
even stranger.

00:09:58.140 --> 00:09:59.860
Alright, Physician Xi,

00:10:00.060 --> 00:10:01.540
stop teasing him.

00:10:02.150 --> 00:10:03.979
Yan, go fill the prescription for me.

00:10:03.980 --> 00:10:05.180
Alright.

00:10:08.980 --> 00:10:11.300
Young Lady Su, your Sixth Brother

00:10:11.420 --> 00:10:12.660
is rather amusing.

00:10:12.980 --> 00:10:14.379
Such honest foolishness is rare.

00:10:14.380 --> 00:10:16.099
Yet he treats you sincerely and loyally.

00:10:16.100 --> 00:10:17.099
Physician Xi,

00:10:17.100 --> 00:10:19.620
you seem unusually attentive
to my Sixth Brother.

00:10:22.820 --> 00:10:25.219
Young Lady Su, could it be

00:10:25.220 --> 00:10:26.220
that you are jealous?

00:10:27.362 --> 00:10:29.402
What nonsense are you saying again?

00:10:29.650 --> 00:10:31.161
I just thought,

00:10:31.162 --> 00:10:33.082
Physician Xi is also a woman.

00:10:35.580 --> 00:10:37.259
If you like my Sixth Brother,

00:10:37.260 --> 00:10:38.980
it is possible.

00:10:43.340 --> 00:10:45.340
So you already knew I was a girl.

00:10:46.180 --> 00:10:47.300
Enough of that.

00:10:47.580 --> 00:10:49.780
Only you treat your Sixth Brother
like a treasure.

00:10:50.512 --> 00:10:51.986
But I

00:10:51.987 --> 00:10:52.824
prefer instead

00:10:52.825 --> 00:10:55.065
soft and sweet young ladies.

00:10:56.060 --> 00:10:57.260
How about this?

00:10:57.420 --> 00:10:59.260
Shall I call you
Little Yuan from now on?

00:11:00.575 --> 00:11:02.415
Then I will call you Ning.

00:11:20.380 --> 00:11:21.460
Master.

00:11:25.475 --> 00:11:26.515
Yu.

00:11:26.780 --> 00:11:28.340
Su Xinyue.

00:11:28.762 --> 00:11:30.219
Do you two admit your wrongdoing?

00:11:30.220 --> 00:11:31.219
We do.

00:11:31.220 --> 00:11:34.300
We were wrong, please spare us.

00:11:37.900 --> 00:11:38.779
Young Master.

00:11:38.780 --> 00:11:39.979
By law,

00:11:39.980 --> 00:11:41.700
malicious slander against others

00:11:42.140 --> 00:11:43.460
is punished by caning.

00:11:43.612 --> 00:11:44.772
The punishment is complete.

00:11:46.740 --> 00:11:49.059
Thank you Captain for showing mercy.

00:11:49.060 --> 00:11:53.100
I will discipline
my household well from now on.

00:12:08.787 --> 00:12:11.107
What you endured today

00:12:11.340 --> 00:12:12.940
is nothing compared to hers.

00:12:13.540 --> 00:12:15.460
If not for the law restraining me,

00:12:16.300 --> 00:12:19.060
I would have you
suffer the same pain she bore.

00:12:21.750 --> 00:12:22.699
Yu.

00:12:22.700 --> 00:12:23.860
Su Xinyue.

00:12:24.527 --> 00:12:25.686
You two spread false rumors

00:12:25.687 --> 00:12:27.847
against Su Jinyuan,
First Young Madam of the Xiao family.

00:12:27.862 --> 00:12:30.862
His Majesty
has granted her name justice.

00:12:31.512 --> 00:12:33.712
If anyone slanders her again
in the future,

00:12:34.087 --> 00:12:35.687
they shall share the same punishment.

00:12:43.275 --> 00:12:44.675
Go back inside.

00:12:44.775 --> 00:12:46.295
Haven't you
embarrassed yourselves enough?

00:12:51.612 --> 00:12:52.732
Su Jinyuan,

00:12:52.980 --> 00:12:54.580
you humiliated me today.

00:12:54.900 --> 00:12:56.995
One day, I will return it double.

00:12:59.625 --> 00:13:02.420
(Half a month later)

00:13:03.820 --> 00:13:06.340
I heard you took over
the garrison for only three days,

00:13:06.650 --> 00:13:09.645
yet you won more hearts
than Luo Yu did in three years.

00:13:10.162 --> 00:13:12.482
With fire burning this high,

00:13:12.900 --> 00:13:13.739
you'd best beware

00:13:13.740 --> 00:13:16.180
of scorching your own family's shrine.

00:13:18.860 --> 00:13:20.979
If I do not gain
the soldiers' trust quickly,

00:13:20.980 --> 00:13:23.540
how can I uncover
the truth of the Xiao case?

00:13:23.860 --> 00:13:26.540
The blood of 30,000 soldiers at Linchuan

00:13:27.087 --> 00:13:29.847
